    <item>
      <title>保险公司寻求私人债务解决方案，万科面临压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-vanke-pressure-mounts-as-insurers-seek-private-debt-solution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于担心中国第二大开发商潜在的流动性压力，几家主要保险公司寻求保护其私人发行的债务，万科公司面临着越来越大的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-vanke-pressure-mounts-as-insurers-seek-private-debt-solution</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顾问表示，印度GDP的惊人增长不仅仅是一次性因素</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/india-s-surprise-gdp-wasn-t-only-one-off-factors-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府高级经济顾问表示，印度上一季度 8% 以上的增长不仅仅是由一次性因素推动的，这表明经济势头强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/india-s-surprise-gdp-wasn-t-only-one-off-factors-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:38:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，李小龙电影制片厂正在考虑出售新加坡电影院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/bruce-lee-film-studio-is-said-to-weigh-sale-of-singapore-cinemas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，橙天嘉禾娱乐控股有限公司正在考虑出售其在新加坡和台湾的电影院，并寻求至少 4 亿美元的资产估值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/bruce-lee-film-studio-is-said-to-weigh-sale-of-singapore-cinemas</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:33:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚保持关键利率稳定以支撑令吉疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/malaysia-leaves-key-rate-unchanged-amid-ringgit-weakness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚周四维持基准利率不变，延长了观望立场，因为政策制定者在通胀和经济增长风险迫在眉睫的情况下应对货币走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/malaysia-leaves-key-rate-unchanged-amid-ringgit-weakness</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:00:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大陆集团在汽车裁员和储蓄方面看到了更高的利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/continental-sees-rising-margins-after-savings-in-auto-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大陆集团预计今年的回报将上升，这主要得益于其陷入困境的汽车部门的改善，该供应商正在裁员并关闭工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/continental-sees-rising-margins-after-savings-in-auto-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德意志银行在房地产危机中取消股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/deutsche-pfandbriefbank-skips-dividend-amid-property-market-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行表示，它不会派发去年的股息，因为它寻求在房地产市场恶化的情况下节省资金，同时向投资者保证，它计划支付额外的一级债券的息票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/deutsche-pfandbriefbank-skips-dividend-amid-property-market-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:05:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市下跌；黄金创历史新高：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员等待美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的进一步证词以及欧洲央行的利率决定，股市下跌。日元上涨，而黄金则将涨势延续至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 22:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
